23 SECTION 2. AMENDMENT. Section 43-23-08 of the North Dakota Century Code is
24 amended and reenacted as follows:
25 43-23-08. License standards.
26 1. Licenses and license renewals may be granted only to persons who bear a good
27 reputation for honesty, truthfulness, and fair dealing and who are competent to
28 transact the business of a real estate broker or a real estate salesperson in such
29 manner as to safeguard the interest of the public, and whose real estate license has
30 not been revoked in this or any other state within two years before the date of
